<h3>Frequently asked questions</h3>
<table>
<tr><td><strong>What skin tones does Medium suit?</strong></td><td>The Medium shade is calibrated for Fitzpatrick skin types III–IV — covering the broadest range of South African complexions including olive, Indian, mixed heritage and light brown skin tones. For fair skin, the Light variant is better matched. For deeper complexions, the Bronze is recommended.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Is blue light protection included?</strong></td><td>The Fusion Water Magic filters cover UVA and UVB. Blue light and infrared protection are covered by ISDIN's Heliocare 360° range. For patients with active pigmentation where visible light is a trigger, Dr. Bangalee may recommend combining with Heliocare 360 Pigment Solution Fluid.</td></tr>
<tr><td><strong>Can I use this during active melasma treatment?</strong></td><td>Yes — this is exactly when it is most valuable. The SPF50 prevents UV-triggered darkening while treatment actives work to fade existing marks. The medium coverage conceals residual pigmentation and improves confidence during the treatment period.</td></tr>
